@startuml
title LowCortisol WebApp - Plan Frontend Bounded Context Layers
left to right direction
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide circle

package "Plan Frontend Bounded Context" {
  class "Domain" as Frontend_plan_Domain <<layer>>
  class "Application" as Frontend_plan_Application <<layer>>
  class "Infrastructure" as Frontend_plan_Infrastructure <<layer>>
  class "Presentation" as Frontend_plan_Presentation <<layer>>
}

Frontend_plan_Presentation ..> Frontend_plan_Application : user actions / state
Frontend_plan_Application ..> Frontend_plan_Domain : models and rules
Frontend_plan_Application ..> Frontend_plan_Infrastructure : API services / adapters
Frontend_plan_Infrastructure ..> Frontend_plan_Domain : resources and mappers
Frontend_plan_Presentation ..> Frontend_plan_Domain : view models

note bottom of Frontend_plan_Application
Detailed class diagrams for each layer are available in docs/diagrams/class/frontend/layers/plan.
end note

@enduml
